==English==
===Idiom===
'''[[don't]] [[cry]] over [[spilt]] [[milk]]'''
# {{idiom}} It is no use worrying about things that cannot be [[rectified]].

===Synonyms===
*[[spilt milk]]
*[[no use crying over spilt milk]]

====Translations====
{{top}}
*Chinese: [[覆水難收]], [[覆水难收]]
*Finnish: Ei kannata itkeä kaatunutta maitoa
*Swedish: Gråt inte över spilld mjölk
{{mid}}
*Japanese: [[覆水盆に返らず]] (fukusui bon ni kaerazu)
*Portuguese: Não chore sobre o leite derramado
{{bottom}}

